{"type": "article", "id": 42885, "title": "Lululemon起诉UA侵权，以及，精工推出可口可乐款挂钟 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2017-07-11T03:19:59Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 3801, "name": "I.T"}, {"id": 3865, "name": "adidas Originals"}, {"id": 13078, "name": "Seiko"}, {"id": 19652, "name": "Line Friends"}, {"id": 22380, "name": "White Mountaineering"}, {"id": 1231, "name": "PUMA"}, {"id": 1530, "name": "Lanvin"}, {"id": 8367, "name": "lululemon"}, {"id": 24721, "name": "UA"}, {"id": 976, "name": "Rihanna"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 20, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170711105841kjszBZpdEXr87IAl.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/designer-luxury/lanvin-hires-olivier-lapidus-as-artistic-director-10942542/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Lanvin 任命法国设计师 Olivier Lapidus 为新的创意总监</strong></a> | Lanvin 正式宣布，法国设计师 Olivier Lapidus 将接任 Bouchra Jarrar，出任创意总监，并负责 Lanvin 2018 年春季女装成衣系列。据消息人士透露，Lanvin 的女装系列订单量近年来一直在以百分比两位数的速度下降，拥有 11 项创新专利、且在互联网时尚上有所作为的 Olivier Lapidus 被寄予了改革 Lanvin 的厚望。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/legal/lululemon-lawsuit-under-armour-sports-bra-design-patent-10942413/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Lululemon 起诉 UA 专利和商标侵权</strong></a> | Lululemon 称，UA 的 Eclipse 运动 Bra 抄袭了 Lululemon 的 energy bra，它拥有两项专利和受到商业服装保护。Under Armour 的设计与 Lululemon的设计“非常相似”，以至于可能对运动内衣属于哪个品牌造成混乱，误导和欺骗消费者。此外，Lululemon 认为 Under Armour 的复制是“故意地，以恶意的方式进行的”，并且要求法院禁止出售有争议的产品。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-scoops/rihanna-new-york-fashion-week-10941678/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Rihanna 将带领 Fenty 重回纽约时装周</strong></a> | Puma 女装系列创意总监 Rihanna 宣布，Fenty Puma by Rihanna 系列大秀将重新在纽约时装周发布。此前，除 Rihanna 负责的首个 Fenty by Puma 2016 秋季系列在纽约时装周发布外，随后两季都在巴黎发布。 </p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/7/seiko-x-coca-cola-1960\" rel=\"nofollow\">日本钟表品牌精工（Seiko）与可口可乐合作推出联名时钟系列</a>，以红、白、黑三色构成的挂钟及闹钟看起来很复古。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170711105304nAji0gh67NkQPxKs.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201707111053047T6hpZtRAQxVdcEf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"http://popbee.com/fashion/fashion-news/i-t-blue-block/\" rel=\"nofollow\">I.T 在香港铜锣湾希慎广场新开了一家全新旗舰店 i.t blue block</a>。除了服装之外，这家店还有美妆用品、生活用品和餐饮，另外还引进了 Another A、American Holic、 InstantFunk、ban.do、Puebco 等品牌。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170711105145yeNPtUnQaAvhW1SZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201707111051451yloWS7U2IbRMzHY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170711105146ZVXU96bEjTIPnrKp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170711105146JyLeYMwRoS4AdhFX.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170711105147bkZrMRaLT4BdSuVi.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170711105146pwl69AYxqSz0JNG8.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170711105147LCywFVajeKZtYWk8.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201707111051477zJWkdSiN2OmBqy1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>让 Brown 变成恐龙、小猪..<a href=\"http://popbee.com/lifestyle/home-and-living/line-friends-jungle-brown-collection/\" rel=\"nofollow\">.Line Friends 最近推出的 Jungle Brown 系列</a>包括毛绒公仔、腰包、儿童餐碟、手机壳和行李牌，很可爱。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170711105213JOgLZ0m5lGT2b7uw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170711105214iS0qhv2tu4DOLyIk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201707111052132ZXYCKyOz6msQBPG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170711105214WYASwDR1Q3pvuyrh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170711105215qoseRPkpGnWrK7Ii.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170711105214cT3gEG2Lr4NdZAfX.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170711105215Ub4mSwkfGalMPF6e.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170711105225BjSygFqViNXTGAve.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667480\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170711105213INxjYXi1hAUF7w59.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667480\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201707111052148fe2ciIgJxoUHjPb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665854\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170711105231zjnhHJEMSl0WfNYu.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2017/07/10/white-mountaineering-adidas-fw17/\" rel=\"nofollow\">White Mountaineering 和 adidas Originals 最新合作系列发布</a>。该系列包括大地色、黑色和白色的风衣、T 恤、帽子等一系列单品，另外还有三双全新的 NMD 、两双搭载 BOOST 的 Stan smith 以及两双 NMD R2s。 </p><p>这个系列将于 7 月 15 日正式登陆 adidas Originals 门店及线下店铺。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170711104933FHdT764cRrjnM5fD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170711104938zUfN6sSvlgeI17bZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170711104938m93Jtn10xI2OlSha.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170711105007jSQRJpg9yPWTiaCz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170711105006hMF4tPjEkZA1zwUe.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170711105007CXfFDTljGWQBVcRu.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170711105007br2MR4eKLQFcBO0C.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170711105004baZxTjYRpfJ1crwN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170711105005qwOM6NuigvnCR8jL.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201707111050057RM9Blh0JxiSTwUn.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201707111050064XrsPxIl0Cd9U6TA.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170711105006yniLCg9Q4RXM2eNV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170711105004Fy6gjEVx0OS9Mp5m.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2017071110500897tnweqOh4rHFxfv.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170711105007fNUzAGsYWFpveTV3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170711105008xVLXZsT76cGHMwhQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201707111050091QIyJsxERnbLqaiP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170711105009CmjQu84HbnXWMlqA.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170711105010ACc78sTK0jpRNzHq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170711105010duB4PUL3kHVXIJj8.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170711105011w3ATrzPfLxsvEZVy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170711105011WIUKA0Ln8TmkDqGO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170711105005jyY37Zd4o5l8x1aN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170711105011co3ISdlGsVi8b0un.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170711105012qRBbs4dTkcC8jZJ1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170711105013XDEzy5VKRsrdmOMu.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170711105013SxaAgTy3R8eP7BMz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170711105013PB5I4roakZ6EcDvb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>位于东开罗的设计师 Dana Frid 设计了一系列<a href=\"http://www.vogue.com/article/fashion-runway-dana-frid-instagram-designer\" rel=\"nofollow\">“恶搞”各大品牌的 T 恤</a>，以其设计的图案配合各大品牌的 logo 或 slogan，像是 Chanel、Dior、Gucci、Versace 等，被绣上“Keep the Snakes Away Unless They Gucci”、“Bitches Want Chanel”、“Die for Dior”等语句，玩味十足。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201707111049036N7FkUO2zVobQlTh.png\" data-ratio=\"1.151376\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170711104903qDE5yOIQ3gFe1Bd7.png\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170711104903L6ZAskvTyzqXuMJ5.png\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170711104904RxtwvMnObmHPSL04.png\" data-ratio=\"0.950570\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170711104904vibPGA9J3kORQxXu.png\" data-ratio=\"0.980469\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170711104914Dk0cU6XpehWgySYC.png\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure></div><p><br></p><p>题图来自：<a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/legal/lululemon-lawsuit-under-armour-sports-bra-design-patent-10942413/\" rel=\"nofollow\">wwd</a></p>"}